<script>
import { defineComponent } from '@vue/composition-api'

export default defineComponent({
  setup() {
    
  },
  
})

import Vue from 'vue'

Vue.mixin({
    methods: {
      capitalizeFirstLetter(str) {
          return str.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + str.slice(1);
      }    
    }
  })
  new Vue({
    el: '#app'
  })
</script>
